> **⚠️ KTU Examiner's Valuation Warning — Common Mark-Losing Pitfalls**
>
> 1. **Forgetting `setDefaultCloseOperation(EXIT_ON_CLOSE)`** — the window won't close on the X button. Lose 0.5–1 mark.
