- ✅ `JPasswordField.getPassword()` returns `char[]` (not `String`) — security.
- ✅ Common listeners: `ActionListener` (clicks), `ItemListener` (toggle), `ChangeListener` (slider/tab), `ListSelectionListener` (list/table).
- ✅ Layout managers: `FlowLayout`, `BorderLayout`, `GridLayout`, `GridBagLayout`, `BoxLayout`. Use them — avoid `null` layout.
- ✅ `JOptionPane.showMessageDialog()` / `showInputDialog()` / `showConfirmDialog()` for quick dialogs.
- ✅ `JTable` needs a `JScrollPane` to display scrollbars.
- ✅ MVC = Model (data) + View (UI delegate / PLAF) + Controller (listener + input map).
- ✅ Always end constructors of `JFrame` subclasses with `setVisible(true)`.
- ✅ **Don't forget `setDefaultCloseOperation(JFrame.EXIT_ON_CLOSE)`** in standalone demos.
- ✅ For large code, implement `ActionListener` in the **frame class itself** to avoid extra inner classes.
- ✅ Swing is **single-threaded** — all UI updates must happen on the **Event Dispatch Thread (EDT)**.

